        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫、姓海明瑞字刚峰。大明嘉靖皇帝驾前为臣。钦奉圣命、解押皇粮回京。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不想行至江中，连日风狂浪大，船只难以行走。闻听此处有一金顶山，真武大"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "帝甚是灵应，不免前去叩求神圣，保佑船只早到京都，交旨覆命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右，看衣更换。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四红文堂、四红大铠、二期牌、门子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。海瑞换衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右，你老爷要到金顶山上拈香，叩求玄天大帝保护船只，早到京都。不用你"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等跟随。你等就在山下伺候，等候你老爷下山便了。回避了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四红文堂、四红大铠、二期牌、门子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四红文堂、四红大铠、二旗牌、门子自两边分下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！想我海瑞，为官清正，因何遇着这样狂风大浪，船只难以行走。唉，玄天"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大帝呀佛祖，保佑弟子阿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "海刚峰奉圣命亲解皇粮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不料想连日里浪大风狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但愿得解皇粮道路安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "早回京复圣命面奏吾皇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哪顾得崎岖路心意彷徨。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "门子→海瑞",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "海瑞→门子",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
