    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "海瑞",
        "老道",
        "耳边厢又听得有人喧嚷"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老道上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老道修行金顶山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙家奥妙师傅传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我、金顶山上老道便是。每日跟随师傅打坐，真心修练。这且不言。我们这山"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上，玄天大帝佛祖甚是灵应，香火十分兴旺。奉了老师傅之命，叫我巡山，要"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有香客往山上烧香，不许穿牛皮底的靴子、鞋子的来朝金顶，怕是佛祖见怪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，话语未了，远远望见有人上山来了，我不免在此等候便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（海瑞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "行半日路不平山顶盼望，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "心恍惚上不去所为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（海瑞跌倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊施主，上山烧香，慢些走哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "险些儿跌下山性命有伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得有人喧嚷"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "施主，上山烧香，慢些走哇。道路难行，只恐跌下涧去呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "猛抬头见道者站在山旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，道爷请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！施主敢莫是上山烧香还愿的吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是，哎呀道爷呀！我行了半日，怎么总不能上山朝顶，是何缘故啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个！施主我请问你脚底下穿得什么靴子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是青缎靴子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么底子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是牛皮底子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪不得施主总不能上山朝顶啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "施主有所不知，只因山上佛祖甚是灵应，凡是山下来的香客，不论烧香还是还"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愿，要是有穿着牛皮底子的靴鞋，纵然走上一天，他也不能上山朝顶进香。我"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劝施主快把这双靴子脱啦，换上布鞋，就能够上山朝顶啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，倒也凑巧，上山之时，我恐山路难走，带着这双旧鞋。待我换上，一同"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（海瑞换鞋。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烦劳道爷引路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看施主倒也心虔，偏偏就带着旧鞋，这是佛祖当时的灵应。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！真是灵应。啊道爷，我这一双靴子，寄存何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我给你放在这山洞旁边，料无妨碍。下山的时候你可想着拿它。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，有劳了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说好说。施主随我朝顶来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海刚峰秉虔心山岗来上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我跟随道爷走脚步慌忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊施主急忙忙一同前往，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老道、海瑞同走小圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不觉得来到了佛祖庙堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "施主请进！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老道、海瑞同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "老道→海瑞",
          "turns": 12
