    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二郎神",
        "八神将",
        "关平",
        "周仓",
        "海瑞",
        "玄天大帝",
        "老道",
        "蛇将",
        "龟将"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（幕启。四云童、八神将、龟将、蛇将、关平、周仓、二郎神两旁侍立，玄天大帝坐高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见烟花片四海云烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尽都是名与利痴心妄贪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此上多感应催劫香烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三十三天我为尊，祥云霭霭护金身。前有三千灵官将，后有五千揭帝神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾神，北极玄天真武大帝是也。嘉靖在位，君王有道，五谷丰收，观见海瑞解"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "押皇粮，海中船只难行，必然前来朝顶叩求。远远望见海瑞来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老道、海瑞同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急急忙忙进庙堂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩求佛祖显灵光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀佛祖啊！弟子海瑞，奉了家嘉靖皇帝旨意，押解皇粮万石向京交纳。只因"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海中难以行舟，叩求佛祖，保佑皇粮早到北京，弟子呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我撞钟擂鼓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "跪在佛殿把话讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊生佛祖听端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "重修庙宇塑容装。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（海瑞抬头看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀老道，这殿内之鼓，是什么皮的呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个！八成是马皮吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀佛祖啊，弟子上山之时，足下穿着牛皮靴子，总不叫弟子上山。你这个佛"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "殿之内的牛皮鼓，难道它是自己到得殿中的吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（玄天大帝指鼓，鼓出殿外。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀佛祖啊，你显灵晚了。佛祖啊，你及早行走，将皇粮解到嘉靖皇上驾前，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我还要与你大大的讨封呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊施主！你疯了吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我疯了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "施主，随我到禅堂吃杯茶去吧。走吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海瑞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老道引海瑞同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "善哉呀善哉！吾神看海瑞却有一片忠心保国。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周仓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在！"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你前去保护皇粮，然后去到嘉靖皇帝驾前讨封，休得迟误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周仓下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关平、二郎神！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平、二郎神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你等带领神兵神将，保护皇粮，休得迟误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平、二郎神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法指。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关平、二郎神同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大德乾坤都一照，妖魔鬼怪岂能逃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄天大帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众神将，收了威严者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "八神将、龟将、蛇将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
